==Dutch==
===Pronunciation===
:*[[IPA]]: /ʋar/ (NL) /war/ (B, Sur).

===Interrogative adverb===
'''waar'''
# [[where]]
#: ''Waar is Jan?''' - Where is John?
# locative adverbial part of a separable pronominal adverb, replacing [[what]]
#: [[waarvoor]]: '''''Waar''' is dat goed '''voor?''''' - What is that good for?

===Relative adverb===
'''waar'''
#[[where]]
#: ''dit is waar hij woont'' - This is where he lives
# locative adverbial part of a separable pronominal adverb, replacing [[what]]
#: e.g. [[waarvoor]]: ''Dit is '''waar'''  dat goed '''voor''' is'' - This is what that is good for.

